{
  "id": 5075532483657728,
  "name": "Enhanced Canvas TextMetrics",
  "summary": "Expand the TextMetrics Canvas API to support selection rectangles, bounding box queries, and glyph cluster-based operations.\n\nThis new functionality should enable complex text editing applications with accurate selection, caret positioning, and hit testing.  Additionally, cluster-based rendering facilitates sophisticated text effects such as independent character animations and styling. ",
